---
title: Bengal Chicken, Chickpea & Green Bean Curry with Rapid Rice & Lime
description: Warm, fragrant and on the table in no time! This curry is a speedy yet satisfying dish, loaded with protein-packed chickpeas, chicken,  aromatic spices and tender green veg. Served with fluffy rapid rice and a zingy hit of lime, it’s a bowl full of comfort with a fresh twist!
